stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> offline
    offline --> connected: handshake success
    connected --> degraded: timeouts / drops exceed threshold
    degraded --> connected: traffic resumes cleanly
    degraded --> offline: silent-close / retry budget exhausted
    connected --> offline: user action: rotate
    offline --> offline: user action: retry
